<item>
            <title>[LU-15549] client doesn&apos;t send layout version if it&apos;s 0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15549</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the client doesn&apos;t set OBD_MD_LAYOUT_VERSION if current layout version is 0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (io-&amp;gt;ci_layout_version &amp;gt; 0) {
                                &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* verify layout version */&lt;/span&gt;
                                oa-&amp;gt;o_valid |= OBD_MD_LAYOUT_VERSION;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;then OST just skips layout version check:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* need to verify layout version */&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (oa-&amp;gt;o_valid &amp;amp; OBD_MD_LAYOUT_VERSION) {
                rc = ofd_verify_layout_version(env, fo, oa);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;all regular layouts are created with version 0, meaning that if client doesn&apos;t notice layout change for a reason (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15300&quot; title=&quot;mirror resync can cause EIO to unrelated applications&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15300&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15300&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; or eviction from MDS), then OST won&apos;t check version even if it&apos;s changed and propagated to OST already. this can result in silent data corruption.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="68626">LU-15549</key>
